title: List of most-liked Instagram posts
description: This list contains the top 20 posts with the most likes on the photo and video-sharing social networking service Instagram. The most-liked post on Instagram is a photo of an egg, which has been liked by over 55 million different accounts as of November 2022.[1][2] The like function has been removed in certain countries, such as Australia, in a trial to reduce the negative effects of 'competition' on the platform.[3]
